Scholarship
Big Metal is offering post-high school scholarships to qualified Crow Tribal members at an initial amount of $75,000 per year under the option agreement and $150,000 per year upon the exercise and approval of a lease(s), starting with the 2013-2014 academic year (this amount is in 2012 dollars and adjusted each year for inflation). Qualified students may apply to the Big Metal Scholarship Selection Committee. Applications are available through the Crow Tribe’s Department of Education, located at Bacheeitche Ave. Crow Agency, MT 59022.
Scholarship applications are due July 15.
