LLC Coal Company Zarechnaya: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 9:05 PM ET
Oil, Gas and Consumable Fuels

Company Overview of LLC Coal Company Zarechnaya



Snapshot People




Company Overview
LLC Coal company Zarechnaya, together with its subsidiaries, engages in coal mining in the Kuzbass region. It offers mine and wash gas coal, flame coal, coal of gas grade, and coal of LoFl grade. The company also provides services, such as geological records making, exploration planning and drafting, geologic prospecting works, geophysical studies, in-mine geophysics, methane drainage boreholes drilling, and underground methane drainage drilling, as well as geological materials preparation for writing-off the reserves, technical, and economic assessment of conditions; and coal-improving services, such as crushing, purification, and magnetic separation. In addition, it engages in extracting m...
LLC Coal company Zarechnaya, together with its subsidiaries, engages in coal mining in the Kuzbass region. It offers mine and wash gas coal, flame coal, coal of gas grade, and coal of LoFl grade. The company also provides services, such as geological records making, exploration planning and drafting, geologic prospecting works, geophysical studies, in-mine geophysics, methane drainage boreholes drilling, and underground methane drainage drilling, as well as geological materials preparation for writing-off the reserves, technical, and economic assessment of conditions; and coal-improving services, such as crushing, purification, and magnetic separation. In addition, it engages in extracting methane from coal beds; developing and manufacturing mining machinery, including roof supports, metal yielding arched supports, metal yielding and rigid trapezoidal, metal crown runners, monorails, arced supports and metal boltings, and monorail and point elements; and provides electric motors overhaul services. Further, the company’s services include equipment maintenance for electric motors, ventilators, voltage transformers, supply transformers, and contactor starter coils; and filling oxygen into cylinders; and turning, milling, metal, and welding works. Furthermore, it exports its end products. It serves heat power plants; and chemical-recovery, energy, and other enterprises in the Russian Federation, Spain, the United Kingdom, the Netherlands, Japan, Korea, and internationally. LLC Coal company Zarechnaya was formerly known as Severnaya-Polysaevskaya. The company was founded in 1953 and is based in Polysaevo, Russian Federation with sub-offices in Kemerovo and Moscow, Russian Federation. LLC Coal company Zarechnaya is a former subsidiary of CJSC DIA Kuzbass.
